koutservice → cartservice (根因)  \nfrontend → productcatalogservice (直接调用)\n```\n\n### 3. **根因定位**\n- **productcatalogservice** 是最下游的异常服务，其延迟直接影响了checkoutservice和frontend\n- **cartservice** 同样是最下游异常，影响checkoutservice的购物车操作\n- 这两个服务都是根因服务，而checkoutservice和frontend是受害者\n\n### 4. **网络vs服务问题**\n从数据看，延迟主要集中在服务处理时间上，而非网络传输时间，因为父服务和子服务都显示相似的高延迟模式。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "tidb-tikv is the root cause due to region_pending performance bottleneck (162.53% increase) causing cascading service delays"}
